avalanche_note: |md
  ### Avalanche Propagation of W[0]
  **W[0]** (0x61626380) enters via the gray **+W[t-16]** edge at W[16].
  W[16] then feeds W[18] via **σ1** (orange), W[19] via the W[17]→W[19] σ1 chain,
  and so on. By W[21], W[0]'s influence has been mixed through σ1 **five times**,
  each application XORing three rotated/shifted perspectives of the value.
  By W[63], **every word** carries W[0]'s fingerprint.
| {
  near: bottom-center
  style: {
    fill: "#FFF8E1"
    stroke: "#F9A825"
    stroke-width: 1
    border-radius: 6
    font-size: 12
  }
}